          FROM config

               date_created,
               last_updated
          FROM install_configuration
         WHERE id = ?

SELECT ia.id,
               ia.display_name,
               ia.installed_app_type,
               ia.install_status,
               ia.app_id,
               ia.reference_id,
               ia.location_id,
               ia.owner_type,
               ia.owner_id,
               ia.install_app_notice,
               ia.is_deleted,
               ia.date_created,
               ia.last_updated,
               app.plugin_id,
               app.dashboard_cards_enabled,
               app.preinstall_dashboard_cards_enabled,
               app.icon_image_url,
               app.display_name AS app_display_name,
               app.app_name,
               group_concat(app_tag.name order by app_tag.name ASC SEPARATOR ',') AS app_tag_name  
          FROM installed_app AS ia
          LEFT JOIN app ON ia.app_id = app.app_id
          LEFT JOIN app_tag ON ia.app_id = app_tag.app_id AND app_tag.name like 'st:class:%'   
         WHERE ia.id = ?
         GROUP BY ia.id
